    {
      "id": "fd0ae9df-3b41-4812-837a-f5bedbb21514",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To circumvent this limitation, the authors propose a Graph Neural Network model that tries to reflect relationships between students. They end up treating the problem as a semi-supervised classification problem where each node represents a student and the node’s label a performance status and an attention mechanism is used to create a single graph representation.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "fd0ae9df-3b41-4812-837a-f5bedbb21514",
